OL,3,CCould Guernsey introduce a tourist tax
OL,4,Cand how would it work?
OL,6,FGuernsey's Tourism Management Board
OL,7,F(TMB) says it welcomes the
OL,8,Fintroduction of a visitor tax as
OL,9,Fpolitical conversations continue over
OL,10,Fthe idea.
OL,12,FCharlie Walker, the organisation's
OL,13,Fvice-chair, explains: "TMB certainly
OL,14,Fsee it as a positive step forward. We
OL,15,Faccept that taxing tourism is a fairly
OL,16,Fglobally recognised initiative these
OL,17,Fdays but one thing we'd like to see is
OL,18,Fthat money then put straight back into
OL,19,Fthe tourism pot."
