OL,3,CCould Guernsey introduce a tourist tax
OL,4,Cand how would it work?
OL,6,FShe believes the extra funding could
OL,7,Fbe used to promote Guernsey better as
OL,8,Fa destination to the UK market and
OL,9,Fthose further afield.
OL,11,FCharlie's comments follow a recent
OL,12,Fpolitical scrutiny meeting where
OL,13,FBethan Haines, Chief Resources Officer
OL,14,Ffor the Policy and Resources
OL,15,FCommittee, stated: "There is already a
OL,16,Fworkstream underway looking at some
OL,17,Fkind of visitor levy, these work
OL,18,Fstreams are already in train and will
OL,19,Fbe brought to the States in due
OL,20,Fcourse."
