OL,3,CCould Guernsey introduce a tourist tax
OL,4,Cand how would it work?
OL,6,FCharlie says it is important to avoid
OL,7,F"over-complicating" how the tax would
OL,8,Fbe collected and that she would
OL,9,Fwelcome politicians consulting with
OL,10,Findustry over the plans.
OL,12,FVarying forms of tourism taxes already
OL,13,Fexist in popular holiday destinations
OL,14,Faround the world and are often
OL,15,Fdifferent from city to city.
OL,17,FIt can be an attempt by local
OL,18,Fauthorities to bring in extra money to
OL,19,Frevamp the area or to tackle excessive
OL,20,Flevels of tourism.
