OL,3,CCould Guernsey introduce a tourist tax
OL,4,Cand how would it work?
OL,6,FAmsterdam charges visitors one of the
OL,7,Fhighest tourist taxes - 12.5% of the
OL,8,Fnet nightly rate in hotels, holiday
OL,9,Frentals and bed and breakfasts.
OL,11,FCruise operators going to Amsterdam
OL,12,Ffor day trips are also charged E14.30
OL,13,Fper passenger.
OL,15,FVenice charges tourists up to E5 per
OL,16,Fnight, although the tax is lower for
OL,17,Fthose outside of peak season.
