OL,3,CCould Guernsey introduce a tourist tax
OL,4,Cand how would it work?
OL,6,FWhile some countries like Greece
OL,7,Fcharge visitors the same rate of tax
OL,8,Fregardless of what part of the country
OL,9,Fthey visit, in many other European
OL,10,Fnations they vary from city to city,
OL,11,Fwith municipal or regional authorities
OL,12,Fdeciding how much they charge.
OL,14,FBarcelona and Paris charge tourists at
OL,15,Fa different nightly rate depending on
OL,16,Fhow expensive the accommodation is:
OL,17,Fstaying on a campsite in Paris will
OL,18,Fcost E1.95 under the tax, whereas the
OL,19,Fmost luxurious five-star hotel will be
OL,20,Flevied at E15.60.
