OL,3,CCould Guernsey introduce a tourist tax
OL,4,Cand how would it work?
OL,6,FSome tourist taxes are included in the
OL,7,Fprice of accommodation, while others
OL,8,Fare paid at the end of a stay or
OL,9,Flevied at the border when a person
OL,10,Farrives in a country.
OL,12,FOn top of any local tourist tax,
OL,13,FChannel Islanders and UK nationals
OL,14,Fwill soon have to pay a E7 visa waiver
OL,15,Ffee to visit any of 30 European
OL,16,Fcountries once the ETIAS travel
OL,17,Fauthorisation scheme is brought in -
OL,18,Fit will last for three years.
