OL,3,CCould Guernsey introduce a tourist tax
OL,4,Cand how would it work?
OL,6,FTourist taxes are also present in the
OL,7,FUK with Manchester becoming the first
OL,8,FBritish city to charge visitors in
OL,9,FApril 2023 as #1 per night was added
OL,10,Fto the cost of city centre stays.
OL,12,FVisitors staying in the Dorset towns
OL,13,Fof Bournemouth, Christchurch and Poole
OL,14,Fall have to pay #2 per night and
OL,15,FEdinburgh is hoping to introduce a 5%
OL,16,Ftax for tourists from July 2026.
